nodes.text: Milo Strander was a Human male GeNode clone trooper, and for a brief time, Stormtrooper. Just after the end of the Clone Wars he was a corporal in Janzor's platoon, and was friends with Wayson Dower.
He served in the Imperial occupation of Kashyyyk, where he and Dower were the only soldiers of their 200-man unit to survive. For his bravery, he was promoted to first sergeant.
